%[text] # Calculus: A Computational Approach
%[text] %[text:anchor:TMP_3624] Purpose: Practice calculus fundamental rules
%[text] Author: Emmanuel Rodriguez
%[text] [emmanueljrodriguez.com](https://emmanueljrodriguez.com/)
